valueI18n.enUS:
The higher of the following:
108% of the total amount of the basic life insurance coverage on the date of the insured's death minus any guaranteed monthly annuity income already paid out; or
The guaranteed cash value on the date of the insured's death;
Plus any accumulated guaranteed and non-guaranteed monthly annuity income and interest;
Plus any non-guaranteed terminal bonus;
Less any policy liabilities.
